# Average or typical

You want to know what is the "average" or "typical" in my sample

> - Mean - *add them up and divide by sample size*
> - Median  - *sort them in ascending order, get the middle value*
> - Mode  - *Most frequent value*

# Average or typical : Example

I throw a two dice 1000 times
